remains at the forefront of innovation, supporting warfighter readiness and strengthening national security.

FY 2027 Plans:
DCSA will pursue research and innovation activities that enhance trust, strengthen national security, and support the
modernization of personnel vetting, industrial security, and counterintelligence and insider threat.




