(Air & Space Operations Center), Project 674587, (Kessel Run Flight Operations), in order to integrate
development within the DAF Battle Network's Theater Air Planning System of Systems. Transfer of this project
increases funding transparency of the project in a standalone funding line as it grows/matures into a reliable
enterprise solution to replace legacy software (PEX).
