architecture priorities to enable Dynamic Mission Replanning and support data sharing/interoperability between
functional and regional AOCs.
-Optimized for operational energy (aviation fuel) use and increased combat capability through operations
software development.
-Enabled the development and scaling of an extensible cloud-based infrastructure and platform as a service
(IaaS/PaaS) hosting platform/enterprise architecture along with the necessary services to support continuous


