Completing the Analysis of Alternatives (AoA) through the service and Office of the Secretary of War's Cost
Assessment and Program Evaluation (OSW CAPE).
Start concept refinement as informed by the completed AoA. Continue targeted advanced technology
development with Virginia Class Block VII and VIII to reduce risk by maturing technologies and maintaining the
