D. Acquisition Strategy
In order to meet accelerated timelines, the QS-ER wing kit is being developed under a sole source contract with Boeing. QS-ER leak resistant bomb bodies are being
developed and procured through an active NAVAIR contract vehicle. QS MOD 3 and CDM mine kits, including target detecting devices, adapters, and other hardware
components are procured via various small contract vehicles or developed internally by the Government. All QS and CDM software is developed and maintained by
Government activities.




